{
    "title": "Você me abandonou",
    "artist": "Velha Guarda Da Portela",
    "composer": "Alberto Lonato",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Você me abandonou</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ô ô eu não vou chorar</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Mas hei de me vingar</span>\n                         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não vou te ferir</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">              G7                     C   C#°</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu não vou te envenenar</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>                            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O castigo que eu vou te dar é o desprezo</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">G7                             C    (C#°)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">    Eu te mato devagar</span>\n          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O desprezo é uma arma perigosa</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7/5-\">Bm7/5-</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É pior do que uma seta venenosa</span>\n           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O desprezo para quem sabe sentir</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Muitas vezes faz chorar</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Outras vezes faz sorrir</span>\n",
